<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.2">
<l>evva nōytavirp pāṉemak kiṟai yiṉṉa kaittuvar vāynila makaḷ</l>
<l>cevvi tōyaval lāṉtiru māmakaṭ kiṉiyāṉ</l>
<l>mauval mālaivaṇ ṭāṭumal likai mālai yoṭuma ṇaintamā rutam</l>
<l>teyvam nāṟava rumtiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who removes afflictions and ills, god to us,</l>
<l rend="indent">sweet[heart] to the great lady Tiru,</l>
<l>He who is able to embrace the beauty of lady earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">a sweet smile on [her] coral lips,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr where comes the breeze which was touched</l>
<l>By garlands of wild jasmine [and] garlands of [garden] jasmine</l>
<l rend="indent">where bees dance, so to waft fragrance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
